tourBios.carHigh: 2013: Re-gained exempt status with rounds of 71-68-73-69 at the 2012 Fall Qualifying School. 2012: Made one cut in seven starts, finishing T38 at the Jamieson WFCU Windsor Roseland Charity Classic. Two time winner of the PGA of Quebec Championship (2008, 2010).
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Won the Quebec Amateur Matchplay Championship in 2003.

dyn.dynBios: Lists The Dye Preserve as his favorite course, Favorite sports are hockey, cycling and snowboarding.
dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Canada was T38th in 2012 at the Jamieson WFCU Windsor Roseland Charity Classic.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T60th in Total Eagles on the PGA TOUR Canada.
